Complete Runfile

  A runfile with all (most) features

Usage:
  run (say|s) MESSAGE [options]
  run ping [--red]
  run (--help | -h)
  run --version

Commands:
  nb`say, s`
    Say something

  nb`ping`
    Respond with PONG

Parameters:
  MESSAGE
    Message to say

Options:
  --color, -c CODE
    One letter color code [default: g]

  --bold, -b
    Show in bold

  --red, -r
    PONG in red

  --help, -h
    Show this message

  --version
    Show version number

Environment Variables:
  COLOR
    Set color code (same as --color)

Examples:
  run say hello
  run say hello -cr --bold